{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-index-tsx","path":"/mysql/5/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://gywlsp.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"72c816ef-962a-5e0c-8ded-f8c2da1beef7","excerpt":"이 글은 inner join, outer join이 무엇인지, MySQL에서 join을 어떻게 사용하는지에 대해 설명한다. Join join은 두 개 이상의 테이블을 관련된 필드들을 기준으로 결합하는 데에 사용된다. MySQL…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>이 글은 inner join, outer join이 무엇인지, MySQL에서 join을 어떻게 사용하는지에 대해 설명한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"join\" style=\"position:relative;\">Join<a href=\"#join\" aria-label=\"join permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p><strong><u>join</u>은 두 개 이상의 테이블을 관련된 필드들을 기준으로 결합하는 데에 사용</strong>된다. MySQL에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">join</code> 명령어로 두 테이블을 결합할 수 있으며 이때 <strong>결합 조건</strong>은 <code class=\"language-text\">on</code> 명령어로 줄 수 있다.</p>\n<p><strong><u>join의 종류와 각각의 정의</u></strong>는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><u>inner join</u></strong>: <strong>결합 조건을 만족하는 데이터만</strong> 선택해 두 테이블을 결합한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong><u>outer join</u></strong>: <strong>결합 조건을 만족하지 않아도 종류에 따라 특정 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택</strong>해 두 테이블을 결합한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><u>left join</u></strong>: <strong>첫 번째 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택한 후, 두 번째 테이블의 데이터를 결합 조건에 따라 매칭</strong>한다<strong>.</strong> <strong>매칭되는 데이터가 없는 경우 그 값을 null로 표시</strong>한다.</li>\n<li><strong><u>right join</u></strong>: <strong>두 번째 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택한 후, 첫 번째 테이블의 데이터를 결합 조건에 따라 매칭</strong>한다<strong>.</strong> <strong>매칭되는 데이터가 없는 경우 그 값을 null로 표시</strong>한다.</li>\n<li><strong><u>full outer join</u>:</strong> <strong>두 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택하고, 결합 조건에 따라 데이터를 매칭</strong>한다. <strong>매칭되는 데이터가 없는 경우 그 값을 null로 표시</strong>한다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c168d290af44a7cfe89cef2c4d9b90cb/b2cef/mysql_5_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.243243243243242%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_1\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_1\"\n        src=\"/static/c168d290af44a7cfe89cef2c4d9b90cb/fcda8/mysql_5_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c168d290af44a7cfe89cef2c4d9b90cb/12f09/mysql_5_1.png 148w,\n/static/c168d290af44a7cfe89cef2c4d9b90cb/e4a3f/mysql_5_1.png 295w,\n/static/c168d290af44a7cfe89cef2c4d9b90cb/fcda8/mysql_5_1.png 590w,\n/static/c168d290af44a7cfe89cef2c4d9b90cb/b2cef/mysql_5_1.png 847w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>다음 두 테이블을 join하는 예제들을 살펴보자.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Residents</code>: A마을 거주자들</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 186px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e68fb27c48dde406045b7d3a8cabb2f2/679d2/mysql_5_2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.10810810810811%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_2\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_2\"\n        src=\"/static/e68fb27c48dde406045b7d3a8cabb2f2/679d2/mysql_5_2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e68fb27c48dde406045b7d3a8cabb2f2/12f09/mysql_5_2.png 148w,\n/static/e68fb27c48dde406045b7d3a8cabb2f2/679d2/mysql_5_2.png 186w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 186px) 100vw, 186px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Animals</code>: A마을에 사는 동물들</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 256px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8806a8819a847dae328908da21253e73/6f3f2/mysql_5_3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.64864864864865%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_3\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_3\"\n        src=\"/static/8806a8819a847dae328908da21253e73/6f3f2/mysql_5_3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8806a8819a847dae328908da21253e73/12f09/mysql_5_3.png 148w,\n/static/8806a8819a847dae328908da21253e73/6f3f2/mysql_5_3.png 256w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"inner-join\" style=\"position:relative;\">Inner Join<a href=\"#inner-join\" aria-label=\"inner join permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><strong><u>Inner join</u></strong>은 <strong>결합 조건을 만족하는 데이터만 선택</strong>해 두 테이블을 결합한다. MySQL에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">join</code> 명령어를 이용해 inner join을 구현할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>inner join을 이용해 <code class=\"language-text\">residents</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">animals</code> 테이블에서 <strong>주인 이름과 반려동물 이름 조합</strong>들을 출력할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> owner_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> pet_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>owner_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 180px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/66083f7586f78cef780a3da8ff3252c9/e9ff0/mysql_5_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_4\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_4\"\n        src=\"/static/66083f7586f78cef780a3da8ff3252c9/e9ff0/mysql_5_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/66083f7586f78cef780a3da8ff3252c9/12f09/mysql_5_4.png 148w,\n/static/66083f7586f78cef780a3da8ff3252c9/e9ff0/mysql_5_4.png 180w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"outer-join\" style=\"position:relative;\">Outer Join<a href=\"#outer-join\" aria-label=\"outer join permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><strong><u>Outer join</u></strong>은 <strong>결합 조건을 만족하지 않아도 그 종류에 따라 특정 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택</strong>해 두 테이블을 결합한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"left-joinleft-outer-join\" style=\"position:relative;\">Left Join(Left Outer Join)<a href=\"#left-joinleft-outer-join\" aria-label=\"left joinleft outer join permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong><u>Left join</u></strong>은 <strong>첫 번째 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택한 후, 두 번째 테이블의 데이터를 결합 조건에 따라 매칭</strong>한다. <strong>이때 매칭되는 데이터가 없는 경우 그 값을 null로 표시</strong>한다. MySQL에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">left join</code> 명령어를 이용해 left join을 구현할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">left join</code>을 이용해 <code class=\"language-text\">residents</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">animals</code> 테이블에서 <strong>전체 거주자 목록과, 매칭되는 반려동물 이름</strong>을 출력할 수 있다. left join을 했기 때문에 <strong>반려동물이 없는 거주자는 pet_name이 null로 표시</strong>된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> resident_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> pet_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>owner_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> resident_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> pet_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">outer</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>owner_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 203px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/af4ba9992753bdf438fc48a598015455/2efce/mysql_5_5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.72972972972974%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_5\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_5\"\n        src=\"/static/af4ba9992753bdf438fc48a598015455/2efce/mysql_5_5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af4ba9992753bdf438fc48a598015455/12f09/mysql_5_5.png 148w,\n/static/af4ba9992753bdf438fc48a598015455/2efce/mysql_5_5.png 203w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 203px) 100vw, 203px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"right-joinright-outer-join\" style=\"position:relative;\">Right Join(Right Outer Join)<a href=\"#right-joinright-outer-join\" aria-label=\"right joinright outer join permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong><u>Right join</u></strong>은 <strong>두 번째 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택한 후, 첫 번째 테이블의 데이터를 결합 조건에 따라 매칭</strong>한다. <strong>이때 매칭되는 데이터가 없는 경우 그 값을 null로 표시</strong>한다. MySQL에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">right join</code> 명령어를 이용해 right join을 구현할 수 있다. <strong>left join</strong>과 <strong>right join</strong>은 데이터를 모두 출력하는 테이블만 다르기 때문에, <code class=\"language-text\">A left join B</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">B right join A</code>와 같다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">right join</code>을 이용해 <code class=\"language-text\">residents</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">animals</code> 테이블에서 <strong>전체 동물 목록과, 매칭되는 주인 이름</strong>을 출력할 수 있다. right join을 했기 때문에 <strong>주인이 없는 동물은 owner_name이 null로 표시</strong>된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> animal_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> owner_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">right</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pet_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> animal_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> owner_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">right</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">outer</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pet_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> animal_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> owner_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> animals <span class=\"token keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> residents\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pet_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 201px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/25d6a5a616386fe7e58453ed1886faae/2ef63/mysql_5_6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.16216216216216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_6\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_6\"\n        src=\"/static/25d6a5a616386fe7e58453ed1886faae/2ef63/mysql_5_6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/25d6a5a616386fe7e58453ed1886faae/12f09/mysql_5_6.png 148w,\n/static/25d6a5a616386fe7e58453ed1886faae/2ef63/mysql_5_6.png 201w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 201px) 100vw, 201px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"full-outer-join\" style=\"position:relative;\">Full Outer Join<a href=\"#full-outer-join\" aria-label=\"full outer join permalink\" class=\"anchor-header after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong><u>Full Outer Join</u></strong>은 <strong>두 테이블의 데이터를 모두 선택</strong>하고, <strong>결합 조건에 따라 데이터를 매칭한다. 이때 매칭되는 데이터가 없는 경우 그 값을 null로 표시</strong>한다. full outer join 결과는 <strong>두 테이블의 합집합</strong> 결과와 같다. MySQL에서는 full outer join을 구현하기 위한 명령어를 기본적으로 제공하지 않기 때문에 <strong>left join과 right join의 합집합을 구해 full outer join의 값을 얻을 수 있다</strong>.</p>\n<p>full outer join을 이용해 <code class=\"language-text\">residents</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">animals</code> 테이블에서 <strong>전체 거주민 이름과 전체 동물 이름</strong>을 출력할 수 있다. 이때 <strong>주인-반려동물 관계는 한 row에 출력되고 주인이나 반려동물이 없는 경우 null로 표시</strong>된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> resident_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> animal_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">left</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>owner_id\n<span class=\"token keyword\">union</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> resident_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> animal_name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> residents <span class=\"token keyword\">right</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">join</span> animals\n<span class=\"token keyword\">on</span> residents<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pet_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> animals<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 222px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0683c39ea052678e1e843620b4d560c4/6bc44/mysql_5_7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mysql_5_7\"\n        title=\"mysql_5_7\"\n        src=\"/static/0683c39ea052678e1e843620b4d560c4/6bc44/mysql_5_7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0683c39ea052678e1e843620b4d560c4/12f09/mysql_5_7.png 148w,\n/static/0683c39ea052678e1e843620b4d560c4/6bc44/mysql_5_7.png 222w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 222px) 100vw, 222px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위의 <code class=\"language-text\">residents</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">animals</code> 테이블을 이용한 join 예제들을 정리하면 다음과 같다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>inner join: 주인-반려동물 조합</strong></li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>outer join</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>left join: 거주민-반려동물 조합</strong></li>\n<li><strong>right join: 동물-주인 조합</strong></li>\n<li><strong>full outer join: 거주민-동물 조합</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/mysql/5/"},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/mysql/5/#join\">Join</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/mysql/5/#inner-join\">Inner Join</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/mysql/5/#outer-join\">Outer Join</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/mysql/5/#left-joinleft-outer-join\">Left Join(Left Outer Join)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mysql/5/#right-joinright-outer-join\">Right Join(Right Outer Join)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mysql/5/#full-outer-join\">Full Outer Join</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"MySQL에서 테이블 inner join, outer join 하는 법","date":"2021-03-16T12:38:27+00:00","description":"이 글은 inner join, outer join이 무엇인지, MySQL에서 join을 어떻게 사용하는지에 대해 설명한다.","tags":["MySQL"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7751479289940828,"src":"/static/b2a3c5f63f54bccf674a77de7e0579b6/f3583/mysql_5.png","srcSet":"/static/b2a3c5f63f54bccf674a77de7e0579b6/630fb/mysql_5.png 300w,\n/static/b2a3c5f63f54bccf674a77de7e0579b6